        "timestamp": "2017-10-12 02:23:51.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\ntca policy has changed based on recent test observation. If this blueprint configuration is default and will be overwritten via clamp/policy - then its okay. Otherwise pls update it per DCAEGEN2-135 for vCPE and DCAEGEN2-137 for vFW.",
