        "timestamp": "2017-10-12 02:32:49.000000000",
        "message": "Patch Set 2:\n\nThe purpose of this submission is NOT to add a perfect TCA blueprint, but have one that will walk through the build process to show the correct plugin URLs.  It will give Alex a starting point to improve the blueprint, including incorporating 135 and 137.",
